OL,3,CLGBT+ Pride parade coming to the
OL,4,CScottish Borders for the first time
OL,6,FThe first ever LGBT+ Pride event will
OL,7,Ftake place in the Scottish Borders in
OL,8,FAugust 2026.
OL,10,FA newly formed organisation, Scottish
OL,11,FBorders Pride, will organise and host
OL,12,Fthe event.
OL,14,FThe event will be free to attend and
OL,15,Fun-ticketed, taking place in
OL,16,FGalashiels on Saturday 29 August 2026,
OL,17,Fand will include a parade, live
OL,18,Fentertainment and exhibition.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
