OL,3,CLGBT+ Pride parade coming to the
OL,4,CScottish Borders for the first time
OL,6,FChair of Scottish Borders Pride and
OL,7,Flocal councillor Fay Sinclair said:
OL,8,F"I'm so excited to be part of an
OL,9,Famazing team of local people working
OL,10,Fto deliver the first ever Scottish
OL,11,FBorders Pride.
OL,13,F"Pride is about celebration,
OL,14,Fvisibility and belonging, so we want
OL,15,Fthis to be an event centred on
OL,16,Facceptance and community.
OL,18,F"We'll be announcing more details in
OL,19,Fcoming weeks."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
