OL,3,CLGBT+ Pride parade coming to the
OL,4,CScottish Borders for the first time
OL,6,FIt is the first of its kind in the
OL,7,FScottish Borders which organisers said
OL,8,Fmarked a milestone for the LGBT+
OL,9,Fcommunity in the region.
OL,11,FThe day will start with a parade,
OL,12,Ffollowed by an afternoon of live
OL,13,Fmusic, entertainment and stalls in the
OL,14,FVolunteer Hall.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/3
